    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Mussel Polypeptide-1 Mussel Oligopeptide-1 Mussel Polypeptide-1) is a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from r-Mussel Polypeptide-1, r-Mussel Oligopeptide-1, and r-Mussel Polypeptide-1. The fusion peptide contains 196 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
